’Ù@a819db65b4eb8633936914f784b0f4c104f2de0499e7bfde2d788e510f0b18e6ÚnTitle: This week in Nushell #108
Path: engine-q
Content:
jt added 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/engine-q/pull/49] very early proof-of-concept git branch completion
, and added 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/engine-q/pull/46] block param types
elferherrera improved 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/engine-q/pull/48] error check on def and alias
, and improved 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/engine-q/pull/40] parse errors for def, let and alias
stormasm created 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/engine-q/pull/47] more block param and build string tests in concert with lists
kubouch 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/engine-q/pull/45] allowed parsing left-unbounded range (..10)
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/engine-q/pull/44] floating point ranges
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/engine-q/pull/43] added stepping support & reversing to ranges
